skopeo: skopeo (a utility for container images and repositories)
skopeo: 
skopeo: Skopeo can perform operations which consist of:
skopeo:  * Copying an image from and to various storage mechanisms.
skopeo:  * Inspecting a remote image showing its properties including its 
skopeo:    layers, without requiring you to pull the image to the host.
skopeo:  * Deleting an image from an image repository.
skopeo:  * Syncing an external image repository to an internal registry for 
skopeo:    air-gapped deployments.
skopeo:  * When required by the repository, skopeo can pass the appropriate 
skopeo:    credentials and certificates for authentication.
